_sText:
Brought you by:

Inflamable Studios



This map, up to 30 players is small and big at the same time. The space between the CT and T spawn
is very short but, if you rush down via the ladders, there can be quite an intense battle on solid ground.
I placed loads of boxes for some cover.


I played this with 20 bots, and i must say, it's pretty intense on the bridge.
It's quite fun, so i hope you guys'll like it. :D
